&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are looking for an Emergency Department Receptionist to join our busy clerical team covering night shifts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We would like to hear from people who enjoy interacting with the public and are passionate about delivering customer service to a high standard in a busy and challenging environment. You will have the experience and knowledge to meet the criteria outlined within our personal specification and job description for this role.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you feel you are the individual we are looking for to join our friendly team we look forward to hearing from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like more information about this role and the hours required then please contact Adam Weston, Service Manager for Acute and Emergency Medicine, on 01582 497065.&lt;/p&gt;
